---
import BlogLayout from '../../layouts/BlogLayout.astro';

// Define all blog post metadata in one place
export const frontmatter = {
  title: "Boxing Timer Champ: Now Available on the App Store",
  description: "Introducing Boxing Timer Champ, the best boxing round timer for serious fighters and coaches. Now available for download on the iOS App Store for iPhone.",
  publishDate: '2025-04-15T09:00:00-07:00',
  heroImage: '/images/blog/app-launch-hero.jpg',
  alt: "Boxing Timer Champ App Launch"
};
---

<BlogLayout frontmatter={frontmatter}>
  <p class="lead text-xl mb-6">
    Boxing Timer Champ is now available on the App Store!
  </p>
  
  <p class="mb-4">
    Boxing Timer Champ is the designed to be a simple, intuitive, customizable, and reliable boxing timer iOS. The app was developed over months of training in the gym with dynamic workout sessions. It is designed for boxers, fighters, and anyone training with precise timing.
  </p>

  <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4">What Makes Boxing Timer Champ Different?</h2>
  
  <p class="mb-4">
    Boxing Timer Champ was built to focus on training. Here's what sets it apart as a boxing timer app:
  </p>
  
  <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-6 space-y-2">
    <li><strong>Fully Customizable Rounds and Rest Periods:</strong> Set your own round duration, rest period, and number of rounds. Design your workouts with precise intervals.</li>
    <li><strong>Audio and Visual Alerts:</strong> Customize warning alerts to prepare for round transitions. Prep yourself and finish strong with audio and visual alerts.</li>
    <li><strong>Clean, Distraction-Free UI:</strong> Large, easy-to-read timer display visible across the gym. Includes a interface in portrait and landscape orientation.</li>
    <li><strong>No Subscriptions:</strong> Boxing Timer Champ offers a free version with ads and an Ad-Free option for a one-time purchase. No recurring fees or senseless subscriptions.</li>
  </ul>
  
  <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4">Developed by Fighters, for Fighters</h2>
  
  <p class="mb-4">
    This timer was created out of necessity. The options for boxing timers aren't great. Many involve copmlicated fields, endless settings, omniscient ads, and plain bad experiences. Boxing Timer Champ was designed to be the champ, the best boxing timer out there. This initial release focuses on a solid timer with custom presets, offering a beautiful experience for great training sessions.
  </p>
  
  <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4">Download Now</h2>
  
  <p class="mb-6">
    Boxing Timer Champ is now available on the App Store for iPhone. Stay tuned for regular updates with new features based on user feedback.
  </p>
  
  <div class="my-8 text-center">
    <a href="https://apps.apple.com/us/app/boxing-timer-champ/id6744783909" class="inline-block bg-green-500 hover:bg-green-600 text-white font-bold py-3 px-6 rounded-lg transition-colors text-lg">
      <i class="fab fa-apple mr-2"></i> Download on the App Store
    </a>
  </div>
  
  <p class="mb-4">
    I'd love to hear your thoughts and suggestions. Feel free to contact me with feedback or feature requests as we continue to refine and improve Boxing Timer Champ.
  </p>
</BlogLayout>
